{
  "name": "PM 06 — Stakeholder Roadmap Digest",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Live deployment checklist\n\nWorkflow: PM 06 — Stakeholder Roadmap Digest\nNodes: 13\nTrigger: Monday 7am\nCredentials/services: Gmail OAuth, Jira API, Linear API, Notion, OpenAI, Slack OAuth\nPlaceholders: #cs-product, #eng-roadmap, #exec, YOUR_ORG, YOUR_ROADMAP_DB, yourco\nEnvironment variables: LINEAR_API_KEY\nExternal webhook setup: not required\n\nBefore activating:\n1. Configure every credential in n8n Credentials.\n2. Replace every placeholder above with live IDs, channels, folders, or database IDs.\n3. Execute once with test data and inspect every node output.\n4. Activate only after the workflow reaches its final node successfully.",
        "height": 440,
        "width": 520,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "live-08ebfbfe02401d5d5acbd82c",
      "name": "Live Deployment Checklist",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        80,
        -140
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 7 * * 1"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
